        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099061 replaced by GO:0098839" , "Rationale: Fig.6: \"Accumulation of the GluR-B subunits in somata and at synapses of GluR-A-deficient mice\"\n- \"...the number of anti-GluR-B labelled postsynaptic densities (PSDs) was about 1.5-fold increased compared to wild-type (Table 2).\"\n\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: \"Accumulation of the GluR-B subunits in somata and at synapses of GluR-A-deficient mice\"" ;
